<div type="edition" xml:lang="san-Latn">
<div type="textpart" n="A"><head xml:lang="eng">Seal</head>
  <ab><lb n="1"/>śrī-tribhuvanāṁkuśa</ab>
</div>
<div type="textpart" n="B"><head xml:lang="eng">Plates</head>
<p part="I"><pb n="3v"/><lb n="37"/>sarvalokāśraya-śrī-viṣṇuvardhana-mahārājādhirāja-parameśvara<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> parama-bha<lb n="38" break="no"/>ṭṭārakaḥ parama-brahmaṇyaḥ śakaṭamanthanī-viṣaya-vāsino rāṣṭrakūṭa-pra<lb n="39" break="no"/>mukh<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ān</corr></choice> kuṭ<choice><orig>i</orig><reg>u</reg></choice>ṁbinas samāhūyettham ājñāpayati||</p>
<p>śrīmati paya<choice><sic>ḥ</sic><corr>ḥ</corr></choice>-pay<choice><sic>e</sic><corr>o</corr></choice><lb n="40" break="no"/><choice><sic>d</sic><corr>dh</corr></choice>i-pratini<choice><sic>bh</sic><corr>dh</corr></choice>i-haihaya-vaṁśe satya-ś<choice><sic>o</sic><corr>au</corr></choice>cābhimāna-saṁpan<supplied reason="omitted">n</supplied>o ni<lb n="41" break="no"/>ja-bhuja-vikrama-śālī poleyana-rājābhidhāno jātas<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> tasya <lb n="42" break="no"/>sūnur anupama-guṇ<choice><sic>ār</sic><corr>aḥ</corr></choice> pitaram anukurvan nannaka-rājas<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> tasya nr̥pa<lb n="43" break="no"/>ter atiratha-dhavala-priya-duhitur āytakaṁbāyāś ca priya-tanayo ya<lb n="44" break="no"/>s tasmai hastinapura-vāstavyāya gaṁgā-pāriyātra-māhiṣmatī-pura-para<lb n="45" break="no"/>meśvara-haihaya-vaṁśodbhava nara-śirodarpaṇa-<sic>dhvajāmālparepoṣaṇa</sic> <pb n="4r"/><lb n="46"/>praśasti-virājamānāya candyana-rājāya mārtaṇḍa-pitāmaha-vikramādi<lb n="47" break="no"/>tya-yuddhamallādi-rājakaṁ vijitya tatra nirbhr̥tya-bhāva-nimittena sarva-ka<lb n="48" break="no"/>ra-parihāram udaka-pūrvakam mānyaṁ kr̥tvā varaṇaveṇḍī nāma grāmo <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>smā<lb n="49" break="no"/>bhir datta Iti viditam astu vaḥ||</p>
<p>Asyāvadhayaḥ|| pūrvataḥ pe<lb n="50" break="no"/>nuṁbaṟṟu| dakṣiṇataḥ penuṁballi| paścimataḥ velmadū<lb n="51" break="no"/>ru| Uttarataḥ dāmarapalli|| kṣetra-sīm<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice> pūrvataḥ <foreign xml:lang="tel">peddakra<lb n="52" break="no"/>lla cinta</foreign>| Āgneyataḥ <foreign xml:lang="tel">premulapadugakaditi nalla jinta</foreign>| dakṣiṇataḥ <lb n="53"/><foreign xml:lang="tel">goraga pannasa</foreign>| n<choice><sic>au</sic><corr>ai</corr></choice>rr̥tyataḥ <foreign xml:lang="tel">muyyūlkuṭṭuna nūjjuṁ jinta</foreign>| paścimataḥ ro<lb n="54" break="no"/>livāyu| vāyavyataḥ <foreign xml:lang="tel">muyyūlkuṭṭuna pedda cinta</foreign>| Uttarataḥ vārama<pb n="4v" break="no"/><lb n="55" break="no"/>palli-sīm<choice><sic>o</sic><corr>ai</corr></choice>va sīm<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice>| <choice><orig>Ī</orig><reg>Ai</reg></choice>śānataḥ <foreign xml:lang="tel">niduva paduga</foreign>| Asyopari na kenacid bā<lb n="56" break="no"/>dhā karttavyā<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> yaḥ karoti sa paṁca-mahā-pātaka-saṁyukto nara<lb n="57" break="no"/>kaṁ gamiṣyati| tathā coktaṁ bhaga<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>tā vyāsena</p>
<lg n="1" met="anuṣṭubh">
<l n="a">sva-dattāṁ para-dattāṁ <lb n="58"/>vā</l>
<l n="b">yo hareta vasundharā<choice><sic>ḥ</sic><corr>ṁ</corr></choice>|</l>
<l n="c">ṣaṣṭiṁ varṣa-sahasrāṇāṁ</l>
<l n="d">vi<lb n="59" break="no"/>ṣṭhāyāṁ jāyate k<choice><orig>ri</orig><reg>r̥</reg></choice>miḥ||</l>
</lg>
<p>yaś ca pālayati sa svarga-pha<lb n="60" break="no"/>lam anubha<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>ti<supplied reason="subaudible">.</supplied> ta<choice><sic>bh</sic><corr>th</corr></choice>ā cokta<choice><sic>ka</sic><corr>M</corr></choice>|</p>
<lg n="2" met="anuṣṭubh">
<l n="a">bahubhir vasudhā dattā</l>
<l n="b">bahubhiś cānupā<lb n="61"/>litā|</l>
<l n="c">yasya yasya yadā bhūmis</l>
<l n="c">tasya tasya tadā phalam</l>
</lg>
<ab>iti|</ab>
<lg n="3" met="śālinī">
<l n="a"><lb n="62"/>sarvān etān bhāvinaḥ p<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice><supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>thivendrān</l>
<l n="b">bhūyo bhūyo yācate rā<pb n="5r" break="no"/><lb n="63" break="no"/>mabhadraḥ|</l>
<l n="c">sāmānyo <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>yan dharmma-setur nr̥pāṇāṁ|</l>
<l n="d">kāle kāle pāla<lb n="64" break="no"/>nīyo bhavadbhiḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="4" met="vasantatilakā">
<l n="a">mad-vaṁśa-jāḥ para-mahīpati-vaṁśa-jā vā</l>
<l n="b">pāpād a<lb n="65" break="no"/>peta-manaso bhuvi bhāvi-bhūpāḥ</l>
<l n="c">ye pālayanti mama dha<lb n="66" break="no"/>rmam imaṁ samasta<surplus>ṁ</surplus>n</l>
<l n="d">teṣām mayā viracito <supplied reason="subaudible">’</supplied>ṁjalir eṣa mū<lb n="67" break="no"/>rdhni||</l>
</lg>
<pb n="5v"/>

</div>
</div>
        
        
      
        
